title: HP Lovecraft Historical Society - uncompressed three albums
description:
HP Lovecraft Historical Society is a group of live-action RPG players dedicated to Chaosium's Call of Cthulhu rule and scenario setting. They went beyond mere players and started to create their own media, including but not limited to music, films and other props.

Here you'll find their three first albums:
- A Very Scare Solstice
- Shoggoth on the Roof
- An Even Scarier Solstice
